sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant LS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Inline as RagasEvaluatorInline
    participant InfAPI as Llama Stack Inference API
    participant Backend as Inference Backend<br/>(Ollama 11434/TCP<br/>or vLLM)

    Note over Client,Backend: Flow 1: Inline Evaluation

    Client->>LS: POST /eval/run_eval<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP plaintext
    LS->>Inline: run_eval(benchmark_id, config)
    Inline->>LS: DatasetIO API (in-process)<br/>Retrieve evaluation dataset
    LS-->>Inline: Dataset rows

    loop For each evaluation row
        Inline->>InfAPI: LlamaStackInlineLLM.generate()<br/>(in-process Python API)
        InfAPI->>Backend: HTTP request<br/>11434/TCP plaintext
        Backend-->>InfAPI: LLM completion
        InfAPI-->>Inline: Response text

        Inline->>InfAPI: LlamaStackInlineEmbeddings.embed()<br/>(in-process Python API)
        InfAPI->>Backend: HTTP request
        Backend-->>InfAPI: Embedding vector
        InfAPI-->>Inline: Embeddings
    end

    Inline->>Inline: Compute Ragas metrics<br/>(answer_relevancy, faithfulness,<br/>context_precision, context_recall)
    Inline-->>LS: Evaluation results
    LS-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP

    participant Client2 as Client
    participant LS2 as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Remote as RagasEvaluatorRemote
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KFPPod as KFP Pipeline Pod
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client2,S3: Flow 2: Remote Evaluation (Kubeflow Pipelines)

    Client2->>LS2: POST /eval/run_eval<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP plaintext
    LS2->>Remote: run_eval(benchmark_id, config)
    Remote->>Remote: Read trustyai-service-operator-config<br/>ConfigMap (base image)
    Remote->>KFP: Create pipeline run<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token

    KFP->>KFPPod: Schedule pipeline execution

    Note over KFPPod: Step 1: retrieve_data_from_llama_stack
    KFPPod->>LS2: GET datasets<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP plaintext
    LS2-->>KFPPod: Dataset rows

    Note over KFPPod: Step 2: run_ragas_evaluation
    KFPPod->>LS2: LlamaStackRemoteLLM/Embeddings<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP plaintext
    LS2-->>KFPPod: Inference results
    KFPPod->>KFPPod: Compute Ragas metrics
    KFPPod->>S3: Write results<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM

    Remote-->>LS2: Job submitted (job_id)
    LS2-->>Client2: Job ID response

    Client2->>LS2: POST /eval/job_status<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    LS2->>Remote: job_status(job_id)
    Remote->>KFP: Check run status<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP Bearer Token
    KFP-->>Remote: Run status
    Remote-->>LS2: Status response
    LS2-->>Client2: Status

    Client2->>LS2: POST /eval/job_result<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    LS2->>Remote: job_result(job_id)
    Remote->>S3: Read results<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP AWS IAM
    S3-->>Remote: Evaluation results
    Remote-->>LS2: Results
    LS2-->>Client2: JSON results
